      <title>新西兰央行鹰派立场不受经济衰退加剧迹象影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-07/hawkish-rbnz-seen-unswayed-by-signs-of-deepening-economic-slump</link>
